    "Description":"Departing frō hence one dais iorney, I came to an other citie named Aiaz, situate vppon two hylles, with a great plaine betweene them, and hath in it a notable fountayne, and therefore diuers nations resort thither as to a famous mart. ... On the toppe of both the hylles, are very strong fortresses...",
