    "NameOfTraveler":"Olaudah Equiano",
    "YearOfTravel":1758,
    "Description":"We then steered for America; but, by contrary winds, we were driven to Teneriffe, where I was struck with its noted peak. Its prodigious height, and its form, resembling a sugar-loaf, filled me with wonder.",
