    "Description":"On Thursday they were off Tangiers, and the hills of Barbary, and Tarifa, and Ceuta, and Algeziras, and Gibraltar; and they were so near the land that they could see those places very clearly, being within the straits; and the same day they were off the Sierra de la Fi.",
