    "Description":"Before reaching this place, there is a lake of salt water, a hundred miles round, and in it are three islands, one of which is inhabited. They passed the night at a place called Cusacana, which was a large town, but half destroyed. They say that Toktamish, Emperor of Tartary, destroyed it; who was afterwards conquered by Timour Beg, and driven out of his dominions, and is now deprived of them; as will be related to you presently. In this place there were many Armenians.",
